songs.title: Elevate (Interlude)

I already know how to touch you, I already know. Because you gotta always add on, you can't bring, can't just do what was done. You gotta always add on, we always build, we always grow, we elevate. It's by elevation, so, the way I touch this now, it's just gotta be like-- like the gods is like, yeah
